{"tid":479542,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[有直播] 港超聯 25/11 - 17:30 - 理文 vs 香港飛馬","createTime":"2017-11-25T08:31:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-25T11:20:33.000Z","uid":66314,"like":6,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"02a9e4e418ce383dd2a9521efc84067cb589c445","tid":479542,"uid":66314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T08:31:32.000Z","msg":"直播Link：<br />\n手機版 <a href=\"http://tv.on.cc/mlive/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftv.on.cc%2Fmlive%2F&d=BV1dIdK0AL8otK5DimM3io9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=4b4e1b61\" target=\"_blank\">http://tv.on.cc/mlive/</a><br />\n網頁版 <a href=\"http://tv.on.cc/live/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftv.on.cc%2Flive%2F&d=BV1dIdK0AL8otK5DimM3io9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=e253feac\" target=\"_blank\">http://tv.on.cc/live/</a><br />\n<br />\n場地: 將軍澳運動場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20171124/photo/bkn-20171124230346214-1124_00882_001_01b.jpg?20171125004249\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20171124%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171124230346214-1124_00882_001_01b.jpg%3F20171125004249&h=808e6174&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40056b737edc34929e3d9acd51bcab0caff18885","tid":479542,"uid":66314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T08:33:16.000Z","msg":"兩軍情報:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>理文</strong></span><br />\n上仗作客廣州燕子崗的理文，最終在佐迪及黃駿軒兩人因傷缺陣下，以一球見負，對於兩名傷兵今仗或未能趕及復出，領隊「馮奇」表示對其他球員投下信心一票︰「上場喺佐迪缺陣下，球隊嘅進攻多少有影響。不過我哋唔想太倚重個別球員，作為替補嘅文家永同史提芬彭利拿上場都有唔錯演出，希望做到任何球員隨時都準備好上陣。」<br />\n<br />\n「馮奇」坦言隊中部分球員的信心因近期戰績受影響，惟寄望他們能夠忘記過去︰「有啲球員嘅信心因為之前輸波受打擊，從而影響表現，但係佢哋係有能力嘅。足球好視乎臨場發揮，假若對手持續強攻，到時就會有空位出現，可乘機反擊，希望球隊踢場好睇嘅賽事畀球迷。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港飛馬</strong></span><br />\n在兩項盃賽及聯賽錄得3連敗後，香港飛馬上仗落後兩球下，憑澳洲前鋒查維斯梅開二度以3比2反勝和富大埔，登上聯賽次席之餘，亦將與榜首傑志之間差距收窄至3分。主教練楊正光坦承，上場勝仗有如「及時雨」︰「每支球隊都會有高低潮，我哋喺銀牌同菁英盃都輸波，能夠贏番場『士氣波』好緊要。我亦吸取咗對流浪場波嘅教訓，檢討邊度做得唔好。」雖然理文最近幾仗戰績並不太理想，「光Sir」提醒球員要提防對手反擊︰「利馬傷愈復出，加上梁嘉恆開始復操，球隊總算逐漸重返正軌，但理文擅於快速反擊，所以後防要有好強嘅紀律去應付。」"},{"pid":"be3b8e2f0910b74039b1dbadccb84c3771360c59","tid":479542,"uid":66314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T08:34:00.000Z","msg":"港超積分榜<br />\n1 傑志 7賽19分 +17<br />\n2 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港飛馬 6賽13分 +2</strong></span><br />\n3 和富大埔 7賽11分 +4<br />\n4 夢想FC 6賽10分 -3<br />\n5 南區 7賽9分 +1<br />\n6 R&amp;F畜力 6賽9分 -1<br />\n7 東方 6賽6分 -1<br />\n8 陽光元朗 7賽6分 -7<br />\n9 <span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>理文 5賽4分 -4</strong></span><br />\n10 標準流浪 5賽3分 -4"},{"pid":"8b03bad882a303fa8a5eedbae9d616b5fb3ba859","tid":479542,"uid":66314,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T08:34:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> = 支持<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>理文</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> = 支持<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港飛馬</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nlike呢個留言 = 支持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>兩隊欖炒</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7360a4d88552ac38640fe922e696a647fcd0474f","tid":479542,"uid":66314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T08:35:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">裁判員:\t湯巨森</span></span><br />\n助理裁判員1:\t羅銘亮<br />\n助理裁判員2:\t庾建峯<br />\n後備裁判員:\t伍偉康"},{"pid":"5494881a458533539946f11cb4869794e891e32d","tid":479542,"uid":66314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T08:36:45.000Z","msg":"評述員： 馮堅成、關家昌"},{"pid":"516f488853939c465dab3af36e09881e0a4e97f6","tid":479542,"uid":92072,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T08:39:27.000Z","msg":"支持我馬贏波 聯賽繼續追近傑x<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7af3469a67e739356f71